HALL COMMENTS: BLOOD DRAWN ON 07-21-1990 Test Results Negative for HIV Antibody by EIA test. : The presence of antibody to HIV (HTLV-NEX) and its association with potential infectivity or the transmission or diagnosis of AIDS has not been established.
